>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/span\"><code>&lt;span&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement deprecatedElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strike\"><code>&lt;strike&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strong\"><code>&lt;strong&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub\"><code>&lt;sub&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary\"><code>&lt;summary&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\"><code>&lt;sup&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>T\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tbody\"><code>&lt;tbody&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/td\"><code>&lt;td&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template\"><code>&lt;template&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tfoot\"><code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/th\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/thead\"><code>&lt;thead&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\"><code>&lt;tt&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>U\n <ol>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"resumo","title":"Resumo","isH3":false,"content":"<p>O elemento&nbsp;<strong>HTML <code>&lt;dfn&gt;</code> </strong>&nbsp;(ou <em>Elemento Definição&nbsp;</em><em>HTML</em>) representa uma instância de definição de um termo.</p>\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n <strong style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">Notas de uso no&nbsp;</strong><strong>HTML5:</strong>\n <ul>\n  <li>O elemento&nbsp;<code>&lt;dfn&gt;</code>&nbsp;marca o termo que será definido; a definição do termo deve ser data em torno de <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/p\"><code>&lt;p&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section\"><code>&lt;section&gt;</code></a> ou uma lista de definições por grupo (usualmente um <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dt\"><code>&lt;dt&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dd\"><code>&lt;dd&gt;</code></a> pareado com o <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dt\"><code>&lt;dt&gt;</code></a>).</li>\n  <li>O valor exato do termo a ser definido é determinado pelas seguintes regras:\n   <ol>\n    <li>Se o elemento &lt;dfn&gt; tiver um atributo title, então o termo é o valor deste atributo.</li>\n    <li>Senão, se contiver somente um elemento <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/abbr\"><code>&lt;abbr&gt;</code></a> com um atributo <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/abbr#attr-title\"><code>title</code></a>, então o termo é o valor deste atributo.</li>\n    <li><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">Caso contrário, o conteúdo do texto do elemento&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-style: italic; line-height: 1.5;\">&lt;dfn&gt;</code><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"> é o termo a ser definido.</span></li>\n   </ol>\n  </li>\n </ul>\n</div>\n<ul class=\"htmlelt\">\n <li><dfn><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories\" title=\"HTML/Content_categories\">Categorias de conteúdo</a></dfn> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Flow content\">Conteúdo de fluxo</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#phrasing_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Phrasing content\">Conteúdo de fraseamento</a>, conetúdo palpável.</li>\n <li><dfn>Conteúdo permitido</dfn> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#phrasing_content\" title=\"HTML/Content_categories#Phrasing_content\">Conteúdo de fraseamento</a>, mas um elemento <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dfn\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>&lt;dfn&gt;</code></a> não deve ser um descendente.</li>\n <li><dfn>Omissão de tag</dfn> None, both the starting and ending tag are mandatory.</li>\n <li><dfn>Elementos pais permitidos</dfn>Qualquer elemento que aceite&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#phrasing_content\" title=\"HTML/Content_categories#Phrasing_content\">conteúdo de fraseamento</a>.</li>\n <li><dfn>Interface DOM</dfn> <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"atributos","title":"Atributos","isH3":false,"content":"<p><span style=\"line-height: 21px;\">Esse elemento inclui os&nbsp;</span><a href=\"/en-US/docs/HTML/Global_attributes\" style=\"line-height: 21px;\" title=\"HTML/Global attributes\">atributos globais</a><span style=\"line-height: 21px;\">.</span></p>\n<p>No HTML5, o atributo&nbsp;<strong>title</strong> tem um significado especial, &nbsp;como mencionado acima.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplos","title":"Exemplos","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Os exemplos a seguir são válidos em HTML5.</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- Define \"A Internet\" --&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dfn</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>def-internet<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>A Internet<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>dfn</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> é um sistema global de redes interconectadas que usam o Internet Protocol Suite (TCP/IP) para servir bilhões de usuários no mundo todo.\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Posteriormente no mesmo documento:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dl</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- Define \"World-Wide Web\" a definição de referência para \"A Internet\" --&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dfn</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>abbr</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">title</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>World-Wide Web<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>WWW<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>abbr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>dfn</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>dt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dd</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>A World-Wide Web (WWW) é um sistema de documentos de hipertexto interligados acessados pela <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>#def-internet<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Internet<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>dd</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>dl</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"resultado","title":"Resultado","isH3":true,"content":"<p><dfn>A Internet</dfn> é um sistema global de redes interconectadas que usam o Internet Protocol Suite (TCP/IP) para servir bilhões de usuários no mundo todo.</p>\n<dl>\n\n <dt id=\"sect2\">\n  <dfn><abbr title=\"World-Wide Web\">WWW</abbr> </dfn></dt>\n <dd>\n  A World-Wide Web (WWW) é um sistema de documentos de hipertexto interligados acessados pela <a href=\"#def-internet\">Internet</a>.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificação</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/text-level-semantics.html#the-dfn-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of '&lt;dfn&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/text-level-semantics.html#the-dfn-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of '&lt;dfn&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recomendação</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html401/struct/text.html#h-9.2.1\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 4.01 Specification<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of '&lt;dfn&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recomendação</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"navegadores_compatíveis","title":"Navegadores compatíveis","isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect3\">\n <div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect4\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect5\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div></div>\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n <table class=\"compat-table\">\n  <tbody>\n   <tr>\n    <th>Feature</th>\n    <th>Chrome</th>\n    <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n    <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n    <th>Opera</th>\n    <th>Safari</th>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td>Suporte básico</td>\n    <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n    <td>1.0 (1.7 or earlier)</td>\n    <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   </tr>\n  </tbody>\n </table>\n</div>\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n <table class=\"compat-table\">\n  <tbody>\n   <tr>\n    <th>Feature</th>\n    <th>Android</th>\n    <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n    <th>IE Mobile</th>\n    <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n    <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td>Suporte básico</td>\n    <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n    <td>1.0 (1.0)</td>\n    <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   </tr>\n  </tbody>\n </table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Elementos relacionados à lista de definições: <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dl\"><code>&lt;dl&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dt\"><code>&lt;dt&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dd\"><code>&lt;dd&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/abbr\"><code>&lt;abbr&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>\n<p></p><p></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Resumo","id":"resumo"},{"text":"Atributos","id":"atributos"},{"text":"Exemplos","id":"exemplos"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Navegadores compatíveis","id":"navegadores_compatíveis"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"O elemento HTML <dfn>  (ou Elemento Definição HTML) representa uma instância de definição de um termo.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<dfn>: The Definition element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"dfn","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<dfn> : l'élément de définition","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<dfn>: 定義要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<dfn>: 정의 요소","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"<dfn>: Элемент определения","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"<dfn>","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/html/element/dfn","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/html/element/dfn/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML: Linguagem de Marcação de Hipertexto"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"Elementos HTML"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dfn","title":"<dfn>"}],"pageTitle":"<dfn> - HTML: Linguagem de Marcação de Hipertexto | MDN","noIndexing":false}}